      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving pinnacle. It features the S54 straight-six engine with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS, delivering a linear power band to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis maintains sharp turn-in characteristics thanks to its MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, while the variable M differential lock ensures optimal traction. Recent maintenance includes a valve adjustment and a comprehensive subframe inspection, ensuring the structural integrity of the rear floor. Finished in a classic colorway, this M3 offers a tactile, analog driving experience with a well-sorted drivetrain and crisp gear shifts.",
      "price": 34500.0,
